{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard_API\">Clipboard API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/read\"><code>read()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/readText\"><code>readText()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/write\"><code>write()</code></a></li><li><em><code>writeText()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Clipboard API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ClipboardEvent\"><code>ClipboardEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/ClipboardItem\"><code>ClipboardItem</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Navigator/clipboard\"><code>Navigator.clipboard</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\"><code>Clipboard</code></a> 接口的 <strong><code>writeText()</code></strong> 方法可以写入特定字符串到操作系统的剪切板。</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>备注：</strong> 规范要求在写入剪贴板之前使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Permissions_API\">Permissions API</a> 获取“剪贴板写入”权限。但是，不同浏览器的具体要求不同，因为这是一个新的 API。有关详细信息，请查看<a href=\"#%E6%B5%8F%E8%A7%88%E5%99%A8%E5%85%BC%E5%AE%B9%E6%80%A7\">浏览器兼容性</a> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Clipboard#clipboard_availability\">Clipboard availability</a> in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Clipboard\">Clipboard</a>。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">var promise = navigator.clipboard.writeText(newClipText)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"newcliptext\"><code>newClipText</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> to be written to the clipboard.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一个<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> ，一旦剪贴板的内容被更新，它就会被解析。如果调用者没有写入剪贴板的权限，则拒绝写入剪切板（reject）</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此示例将剪贴板的内容设置为字符串“&lt;empty clipboard&gt;”。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clipboard<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">writeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"&lt;empty clipboard&gt;\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* clipboard successfully set */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">/* clipboard write failed */</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/clipboard-apis/#dom-clipboard-writetext","title":"Clipboard API and events"}],"query":"api.Clipboard.writeText"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Clipboard.writeText","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"Clipboard 接口的 writeText() 方法可以写入特定字符串到操作系统的剪切板。","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Clipboard.writeText()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/clipboard/writetext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/clipboard/writetext/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard","title":"Clipboard"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Clipboard/writeText","title":"Clipboard.writeText()"}],"pageTitle":"Clipboard.writeText() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}